{
  "page": "Jon Myre",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Myre\" title=\"House Myre\"><img alt=\"House Myre 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Myre_2.svg/50px-House_Myre_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Myre_2.svg/75px-House_Myre_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c9/House_Myre_2.svg/100px-House_Myre_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Captain</span><br />Jon Myre<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Pinchface</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Myre\" title=\"House Myre\"><img alt=\"House Myre 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Myre_2.svg/50px-House_Myre_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Myre_2.svg/75px-House_Myre_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c9/House_Myre_2.svg/100px-House_Myre_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nPinchface Jon</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nCaptain<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Myre\" title=\"House Myre\">House Myre</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Jon Myre</b>, known as <b>Pinchface Jon Myre</b>, is a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Myre\" title=\"House Myre\">House Myre</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jon_Myre&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jon_Myre&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Pinchface Jon brings a dozen longships in support of <a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron Greyjoy</a> after he declares himself <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Isles_and_the_North\" title=\"King of the Isles and the North\">King of the Isles and the North</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> He supports Euron at the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot_on_Old_Wyk\" title=\"Kingsmoot on Old Wyk\">kingsmoot on Old Wyk</a>, where he trades insults with <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jon_Myre&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Jon feasts in the ruins of a castle near the <a href=\"/index.php/Arbor\" title=\"Arbor\">Arbor</a> with some of Euron's men, and he takes part in mocking <a href=\"/index.php/Aeron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Aeron Greyjoy\">Aeron Greyjoy</a> when the latter is brought up from the hold of the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Silence\" title=\"Silence\">Silence</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jon_Myre&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Jon</b>: This girl forgets herself. <a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Balon Greyjoy\">Balon</a> let her believe she was a man.<br />\n<b>Asha</b>: Your father made the same mistake with you.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Jon and <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jon_Myre&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_11\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 11\">Chapter 11</a>, The Kraken's Daughter.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_18\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 18\">Chapter 18</a>, The Iron Captain.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/The_Forsaken_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"The Forsaken (The Winds of Winter)\">The Forsaken</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403123729\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.088 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.276 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 823/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10951/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 9727/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1268/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2293/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.32 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  260.351      1 -total\n 95.99%  249.912      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.07%  247.526      1 Template:Infobox\n 14.20%   36.979     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.78%   15.050      5 Template:Infobox_label\n  4.51%   11.751      5 Template:Ref\n  2.88%    7.503      5 Template:Ref/core\n  0.88%    2.278      1 Template:References\n  0.76%    1.986      1 Template:Quote\n  0.72%    1.865      1 Template:Warning/twow\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:5349-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403123729 and revision id 295798\n -->\n",
